						               													<description>Crazy Adjudgement is a party boardgame produced by Taiwan MJBD Games in 2009. Players play the dual role of officials and criminals during the game. Through a battle of wits and lucks between officials and criminals, the final winner will be determined.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is played over several rounds.Each round is divided into six phases(For example with 4 players)&amp;#239;&amp;#188;&amp;#154;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Phase 1&amp;#239;&amp;#188;&amp;#154;determine the role (citizen&amp;#227;&amp;#128;&amp;#129;detective&amp;#227;&amp;#128;&amp;#129;6 officials and 10 criminals)&amp;#10;Each player receives one random purple cards and four random black cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Phase 2&amp;#239;&amp;#188;&amp;#154;catch the criminal&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player who hold the citizen card can accuse any 1 criminal of the 10 criminals. The player who hold the detective card will catch the criminal. He guesses which player hold the criminal card. If he guesses correct. The player who hold the criminal card will be punished.Otherwise the player who hold the detective card will be punished.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Phase 3&amp;#239;&amp;#188;&amp;#154; adjudge the criminal&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player who holds the judgment officer (one of the officials) card judges the criminal. He draws 1 card of the green card deck. The card will determine the result of punishment.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Phase 4&amp;#239;&amp;#188;&amp;#154;replace the criminal&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player who will be punished can choose 1 of the 2 Joker cards.If he choose red card.he draws 1 card of the red card deck.The card will change the result of punishment. If he choose blue card.he draws 1 card of the blue card deck.The card will change the criminal.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Phase 5&amp;#239;&amp;#188;&amp;#154; punish the criminal&amp;#10;When the criminal is finally determined. The player who is the criminal will be punished. The player who hold the execution officer(one of the officials)card will punish the criminal.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Phase 6&amp;#239;&amp;#188;&amp;#154;ending the round&amp;#10;The player who is the criminal is the loser and the dealer next round. Repeat the above steps to enter the next round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
